@startuml project-lifecycle
title Infrastructure Project Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft : Project Scoped (Proposed)

Draft --> Requested : Submitted for Review
Requested --> Approved : Funding & Geo-Coverage Confirmed

state Approved {
  [*] --> Active
}

Active --> Suspended : Funding Pause / Policy Breach
Active --> Deprecated : Project Completed / Superseded

Deprecated --> Archived : Historical Outcome record
@enduml
